<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" version="2.0"><channel><title>界面快报</title><link>https://jiemian.com/</link><description>界面快报</description><docs>http://www.rssboard.org/rss-specification</docs><generator>python-feedgen</generator><image><url>https://res.jiemian.com/assets/wap/common/img/jm-new-logo.png</url><title>界面快报</title><link>https://jiemian.com/</link></image><lastBuildDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 13:30:04 +0800</lastBuildDate><pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 13:30:04 +0800</pubDate><item><title>《哪吒之魔童闹海》总票房超《指环王：王者无敌》，进入全球影史票房榜前31</title><link>https://www.jiemian.com/article/12328905.html</link><description><![CDATA[<div class="article-content"><p>据灯塔专业版全球票房榜显示，截至2月10日，影片《哪吒之魔童闹海》总票房（含预售）突破11.38亿美元，超过《指环王：王者无敌》，进入全球影史票房榜前31名。</p>
